{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 100986, "create_time": 1651837765, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "我认为是自然选择的结果。如果病毒把宿主杀死了，那么病毒自己也活不了。如果病毒把宿主搞得重病卧床不起，那么宿主就没法把病毒传染给更多的人了。", "timestamp": 1651837765}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 100998, "create_time": 1651838475, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "按照达尔文的理论，是随机的", "timestamp": 1651838475}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 101000, "create_time": 1651838523, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "随机的。现代组织和医学不存在使得人只能靠“死不了”来帮助病毒传播的环境。", "timestamp": 1651838523}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 101002, "create_time": 1651838587, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Bob: 按照达尔文的理论，变异是随机的，但进化是有方向的", "timestamp": 1651838587}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 101003, "create_time": 1651838672, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Carol: 病毒造成的症状更轻→感染者更不容易被发现、隔离→病毒更容易传播", "timestamp": 1651838672}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 101022, "create_time": 1651839850, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "赞同Alice", "timestamp": 1651839850}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 101035, "create_time": 1651840255, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 但是当社会对原始毒株就没有能力防控时或者不再防控时，感染者似乎并没有因症状更轻而受到更少传播限制", "timestamp": 1651840255}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 101040, "create_time": 1651840392, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 症状轻的人活蹦乱跳，可以像平常一样出去吃喝玩乐，到处传播病毒。症状重的人恨不得一天到晚躺在床上睡觉，相当于自觉的居家隔离了。你想想自己得重感冒的时候是什么感觉就知道了。", "timestamp": 1651840392}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 101540, "create_time": 1651861450, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Alice: 可是新冠不太一样，因为人类对它的关注十分细致和及时，你所说的“病毒把宿主搞得卧床不起”的情况，也会被及时发现的，并不会出现“虽然有的变种是轻型有的是重型，但我们所发现的变种都是轻型”的情况吧", "timestamp": 1651861450}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 101541, "create_time": 1651861585, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Alice: 有道理🤔所以传播开来的都是轻症…", "timestamp": 1651861585}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 101543, "create_time": 1651861664, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "但这仍然不能解释“为什么最近被发现的毒株都是轻型”，如果有一粒新的毒株会导致重症，重症病人就诊时做个核酸不就被发现了吗？", "timestamp": 1651861664}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 101655, "create_time": 1651887968, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Bob: “最近被发现的毒株”多得是，每天被上传的病毒基因序列非常多，症状肯定有轻有重，只有少数的毒株会被人们关注、命名。", "timestamp": 1651887968}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 101657, "create_time": 1651888009, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "“我们所发现的变种都是轻型”并不是这样的。应该说“我们所发现的就行的变种都是轻型”", "timestamp": 1651888009}], "create_time": 1651837560, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1651888009, "likenum": 6, "n_attentions": 6, "n_comments": 13, "pid": 36775, "poll": null, "reply": 13, "text": "为什么原始毒株进化到奥密克戎，严重性下降而传染性升高呢。严重性下降是完全随机的还是自然选择性的", "timestamp": 1651837560}}